title: NFL Around the League: September 6th, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: September 6th, 2013
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling - breaks down the Denver Broncos' blowout win in their season opener against the Baltimore Ravens. Despite Peyton Manning's historic game, Wesseling tells you what leaves him unimpressed. The crew also gives you their hero picks on top of their Week 1 game predictions. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL .
